title: Down Syndrome Treatment and Therapy pack 2 Text files
description:
Down Syndrome (DS) Treatment and Therapy pack

Many items proven to help kids with DS (and that have helped my kid!).

THIS PACK is pack 2: 
E-books and text files (some refer to videos in pack 3)


THIS PACK Topics: 

1) Breastfeeding help for infants with DS


2) e-Books of natural treatments and supplements for DS

3) Oral Motor Therapy files



Please see packs 1 and 3 for

Sound Therapy to help sensory processing and working memory

Targeted Nutritional Intervention

Music Therapy (Mozart) to raise Growth Hormone and speed healing

Oral Motor Therapy videos

Speech Therapy videos



These approaches are best if used together
